                        <interp inst="t18410614-name-347" type="given" value="MICHAEL ALLEN"></interp>MICHAEL ALLEN JANE</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the Park with a lady—I had a hand<lb></lb>kerchief, and lost it out of my coat-pocket—this is it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Herbert's Defence.</hi> I never met this young man before—I do not know him.</p>
